# Installation instructions

Shell commands:

    $ cd google-play-services_lib/
    $ android update project -p .
    $ ant debug
    $ cd ../v7-appcompat_lib/
    $ android update project -p .
    $ ant debug
    $ cd ../glSatellite/
    $ android update project -p .
    $ ant debug install

